The paper deals with influencer marketing and online learning, which are topics related to social networks and machine learning. Therefore, cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is the most likely category. The paper also involves optimization and decision making, which are topics covered in cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The Independent Cascade model used in the paper is a popular model in cs.SOC (Computational Social Science), which is another likely category. Finally, the paper involves data analysis and simulations, which are topics covered in cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
